t i hodet, og truet med hagle av en fullstendig spr\u00f8 fyr. Kollegaen min vurderer n\u00e5 \u00e5 skaffe seg skuddsikker vest for \u00e5 bruke p\u00e5 jobb, sier Helgemo."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "4c5a18adfc314258d6f3f24707b5414b69d73ce123f6eb2fe9384a57f3d77112"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-05-13T23:44:06.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Taxisj\u00e5f\u00f8r Ingunn Helgemo har kategorisert plagsomme passasjerer."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article8666073.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Taxit03.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/8103b41d8742cada16a920d01383a12103fb5151.jpg?595039c2"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Disse typene kan havne i baksetet -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "8103b41d8742cada16a920d01383a12103fb5151"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "society"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["opplevd", "sj\u00e5f\u00f8ren", "pr\u00f8ver", "taxisj\u00e5f\u00f8r"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["norgestaxi", "ingunn helgemo", "adresseavisens"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/trondheim"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article8666073.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Taxit03.jpg"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.n